{"tid":1898122,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【財政預算案2020】政府推定息按揭貸款　10年期年利率為2.75%","createTime":"2020-02-26T03:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T20:03:05.000Z","uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7e543d77fb8a3189b4944ad6e253d816e60697","tid":1898122,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"為增加準業主的貸款選擇，減低他們面對利率波動的風險。財政司司長陳茂波宣讀新一份財政預算案時，表示香港按揭證券公司將推出試驗計劃，透過銀行提供上限為1,000萬元，年利率分別為2.75%、2.85%及2.95的10、15及20年期的定息按揭貸款。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，計劃的總貸款額為10億港元，會視乎市場反應再作檢討。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為提供更多退休投資項目，香港年金計劃的最低投保年齡由六十五歲降至六十歲，令市民可以按需要及早參與，香港年金公司會盡快公布詳情。"},{"pid":"476ca45b01d11c117afeec143481d2bc16a3b1ed","tid":1898122,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"2.75%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9625bd6c976e0e5552fb3ec95bf85644654ccad6","tid":1898122,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"係咪恆常政策...咁好多呼吸PLAN既人發發"},{"pid":"707298fc7f07a699ca98e73de4433ea8a66729dc","tid":1898122,"uid":37063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"搵笨plan"},{"pid":"7b6ccb08539669b46e503c4445c8cbe35ca8adcb","tid":1898122,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39b6af6f9ac8d43a9d36aa6b24da99c4d6bd0be7","tid":1898122,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6ccb08539669b46e503c4445c8cbe35ca8adcb","tid":1898122,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"如果某一日P仔升到勁高係咪可以轉過去輸打贏要"},{"pid":"6e24fd6ed9399ea12707eb95e5352728d8e20878","tid":1898122,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6ccb08539669b46e503c4445c8cbe35ca8adcb","tid":1898122,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike